summary: This mod is a conversion of Latex Corset Armor by nakrulzto the CHSBHC body
descriptionHtml:
```````[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/348rivk.jpg[/IMG]```````


`````````````````[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/2rgm8ti.jpg[/IMG]`````````````````
This mod adds the latex armor made by nakrulzto to the game. It is a light armor and has an armor value equal to dragonscale gears.The armor can be crafted at the forging station under LEATHER and MISC section. Or if you decide to cheat then open console with ~ then type: help "latex" then use player.additem [item number] [amount]. Please make sure you have CBBE textures installed AND skeleton prior to using this. If you don't have the skeleton support your game WILL CRASH. You have been warned ;) You will also NEED HDT heels system installed. Please refer to the requirements section.


`````````````````[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/28mnzb5.jpg[/IMG]`````````````````

-XP32 Maximum Skeleton -XPMS by xp32
-Textures that will fit the CHSBHC body
-HDT heels system
for colour variation Latex Corset Color Changer(http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49350/?)
